"{\"uid\": \"forbes.com-sites-mikeosullivan-2024-07-25-france-agrees-to-a-political-truce-as-the-olympics-approaches\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByMike O'Sullivan, Former Contributor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 39, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ByMike O'Sullivan\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 17}, {\"ngram\": \"Former Contributor\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 37}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French president Emmanuel Macron has declared that he will wait till after the Olympics to form a government, partly we suspect in the hope that he also hopes for the Nouveau Front Populaire (NFP) grouping to come apart.\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_Front_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9829156082440914, \"rank\": 0.01738050900062388, \"text\": \"Front Populaire\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_Front_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_Front_(France)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"a government\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 149}, {\"ngram\": \"the hope\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"NFP\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically, he has called for a political 'truce' during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a political 'truce\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, in the last week there are signs of new coalition dynamics.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last week\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"signs\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"new coalition dynamics\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Importantly, Ya\\u00ebl-Braun-Pivet has been re-elected as the speaker of the Assembly in a vote where the NFP and Republicans have supported her, and where the NFP have garnered 12 of 22 positions in the Assembly (like the committee chairship in the Senate etc - the NFP have two Assembly vice-presidents and the chair of the finance committee).\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"score\": 0.996577430436766, \"rank\": 0.0029697717684148495, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999953416392418, \"rank\": 3.840724037003097e-06, \"text\": \"NFP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"score\": 0.9998635936559064, \"rank\": 0.00013361237032698205, \"text\": \"Republicans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\"}, {\"beg